<%- include("background.ejs") %>

<style>
    body {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        color: #333;
    }

    .dharali-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(47, 69, 7, 0.7), rgba(47, 69, 7, 0.7)), url('https://placehold.co/1500x500/7A8B9A/7A8B9A') no-repeat center center/cover;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .dharali-hero h1 {
        font-size: 3.5em;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }

    .dharali-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 40px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .disaster-description {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .disaster-description h2 {
        color: #d32f2f; /* A color to signify urgency/disaster */
        font-size: 2em;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .disaster-description p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #555;
    }

    .response-section {
        background-color: #e8f5e9;
        border-left: 5px solid #2f4507;
        padding: 30px;
        margin: 40px 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .response-section p {
        font-size: 1.3em;
        color: #2f4507;
        margin: 0 0 25px 0;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .response-section span {
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .aid-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .aid-list li {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .aid-list li::before {
        font-size: 1.5em;
        margin-right: 15px;
    }
    
    /* Unique icons for each item */
    .aid-list .shelter::before { content: '‚õ∫'; }
    .aid-list .wash::before { content: 'üßº'; }
    .aid-list .utensils::before { content: 'üç¥'; }
    .aid-list .blankets::before { content: 'üß£'; }
    .aid-list .needs::before { content: 'üõçÔ∏è'; }
    .aid-list .lights::before { content: 'üí°'; }

    .gallery-section h3 {
        color: #2f4507;
        font-size: 2.2em;
        margin-top: 50px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .gallery-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .gallery-item img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 10px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .gallery-item img:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    
    .call-to-action {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 50px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-top: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .call-to-action p {
        font-size: 1.3em;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .call-to-action .hashtags {
        font-size: 1.1em;
        color: #2f4507;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>

<div class="dharali-hero">
    <h1>Mountain Forum Himalayas Makes Its Way to Dharali, Uttarkashi</h1>
</div>

<div class="dharali-container">
    <div class="disaster-description">
        <h2>A Village Swept Away by Catastrophe</h2>
        <p>Homes, markets, even the sacred Kalp Kedar temple ‚Äî all swept away in the fury of water and debris. Families are left with nothing but loss and despair.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="response-section">
        <p>In this darkest hour, <span>Mountain Forum Himalayas</span> stands with Dharali, bringing essential aid to the affected families:</p>
        <ul class="aid-list">
            <li class="shelter">Shelter kits</li>
            <li class="wash">Wash &amp; Hygiene kits</li>
            <li class="utensils">Utensils</li>
            <li class="blankets">Blankets</li>
            <li class="needs">Daily Needs</li>
            <li class="lights">Solar Lights</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="gallery-section">
        <h3>Glimpses of Hope from Dharali</h3>
        <div class="gallery-grid">
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="dharali1.jpg" alt="Relief Efforts in Dharali 1">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="dharali2.jpg" alt="Relief Efforts in Dharali 2">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="dharali3.jpg" alt="Relief Efforts in Dharali 3">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="call-to-action">
        <p>Together, let‚Äôs rebuild hope for Uttarkashi.</p>
        <p class="hashtags">#SaveDharali #UttarkashiFlood #MountainForumHimalayas #DisasterRelief</p>
    </div>

</div>

